[node name="Level5" type="Node3D"]
editor_description = "Room 05 — The Gap. FloorNear and FloorFar are split by a 6m open pit (no floor geometry between them). A normal kick can spin the near gear pair, but only a Final Kick burst (hold past full charge) has enough range to clear the pit and reach the far gear pair. GREYBOX FIRST PASS — pit width and burst_impulse on the Ball are unverified numbers, not yet playtested; expect to retune both in-editor."

